        <mxCell id='note' value='Runs on push to main and on PRs targeting main. All jobs run in parallel except E2E which depends on build.' style='rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;dashed=1;' vertex='1' parent='1'>
